0 Param data.1 string m_text: Wow, where'd you learn about this path?
Who cares, hurry up! Someone'll see us!
We need to get you far away from here!
Huh? Why do I need to get away?
You will, I promise. So don't go getting yourself killed.
Our orders are to kill him. No messing around.
There can only be one sovereign.
But do we really have to kill him?
You want to defy a direct order of the minister?
He just got unlucky, that's all.
He'll be the sovereign too, all right—in the next life.
Pray for his soul if you want.
Fine. Let's get this over with.
It's time for you to go too, Soju.
What's wrong? Why are you just standing there?
Please, fighting will only make it worse.
Sara... I need to find Sara!
Was that a glimpse of Soju's past, before he became the Night Devil?
What are you trying to tell me? Do you want me to retrace your steps?
You hear the news? Our guy got himself killed.
Yeah. Stabbed him with a knife.
And he looked so innocent. You never can tell.
Can't let your guard down around anyone these days.
Whichever one of you was not chosen was to be marked for death. A sacrifice to celebrate the new sovereign's ascension.
I know neither you nor Sara want that. You have every right to hate us for what we've done.
Feed that hatred, and use it to raze this realm to the ground.
Find your own way until then. Survive.
As far as they'll know, you slipped into the river and drowned while trying to escape.
There's a village of outcasts not far from here. You can disappear there.
Remember, above all else, you must survive!
Huh? Wait a sec, you're not one of them.
I tried to steal the stuff they got from robbing people.
I just wanted to sell it to get some food. That's all! I swear, that's all!
But those guys, they won't stop chasing me!
Just tell them you didn't see me! Okay?
You! Over there! You didn't see another snot-nosed punk run by, did ya?
I can tell you're an honest kid.
Cause you can't bluff to save your life.
Kid's honest, I'll give him that.
Hey! Grab 'em both and throw 'em into the Pit.
We can always find a use for a kid. Cool your heels down there until we need you.
Do you even have a home?
Tears sap your strength. They make you weak.
And I won't be weak any longer. I'm going to survive.
What's the point? You think people like us can ever be happy?
I don't know, but I plan to stay alive long enough to find out.
Fine...I won't cry either. I'll be strong.
What's that voice? Where's it coming from?
Don't be stupid. You look alive to me.
Well, I'm not. You've just crossed over.
To the place all souls go. The Beyond.
You can hear me and pass through the Veil.
That's unusual. For the living, anyway.
I thought people get reincarnated after they die.
Don't look at me, that's what I thought too. But here I am. I wonder why.
Maybe it's because I'm still angry.
I got tricked and thrown down here in the Pit. Then I died.
I think I might want to make the ones who did this to me suffer.
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.
Whoops, never mind. That's just you.
You ever think about how tasty rocks look?
AH! Don't yell like that, I'm trying to sleep.
You promised me you'd survive, right?
I want to live...but death seems so...easy.
Hang in there, Ikoko. I'll get us out of this.
We're gonna make it through this.
No more waiting. We're getting out of here.
You really gonna let these brats join our crew?
Why not? We were just like them once.
We're thieves. We take from others. Fortunes, lives, it doesn't matter.
Follow me, and I'll teach you how to get by. First lesson: do anything to survive.
Heh. Those are the eyes of a killer. You've got potential, kid.
I swore I'd never give up. I'll do it. I'll join you.
You've got your first job, kid.
Your prey is in those woods. Start hunting.
You came here to kill me, didn't you?
You gonna kill me, or what?
I don't have a reason to!
You said you'd do anything to survive, didn't you!?
Why chase me if you weren't gonna kill me?
I told them it was pointless! You'd never be one of us!
They told me to test you.
But look at you. You don't have the stomach to do what we do.
I even ate that disgusting crap because of you!
I'll kill you here and now! Cross over, for all I care!
Oh I'm gonna enjoy killing you.
Crap! This is a monster den!
I like it here. I don't wanna die.
Either way, one of you was dying. We only had room for one.
That brat wanted to join us so he could find a way out of this hellhole.
How stupid is that? Come on, kid, let's go.
You're not gonna pray for him?
You think we need friends here?
It's every man for himself. Don't forget it.
Remember how you ended up here in the first place.
You were betrayed by your friends! They tried to have you erased!
Deny it all you want. It won't change anything.
The boy who tricked me is dead.
I'm glad I met you, Soju.
This world is full of people who don't deserve life...and the people who suffer because of them.
The shadows of the capital. That's where we make our way.
